  <div class="prose flow">
    <h1 class="center">Welcome to the <%= @course.title %> Course</h1>

    <p class="center">The course is structured in a specific way to easily navigate
    and focus on specific areas of focus one-at-a-time. You are more
    than weclcome to jump around but we highly encourage you follow the
    flow unless you are looking for a specific pieve of information.</p>

    <p class="center">A course is broken up into many parts which you navigate to. At
    the highest level are Segments, then each Segment is broken down into
    Levels, and finally each Level will contain a variaty of "books".
    The books are where all the content is stored and where you will truly
    begin learning. As you navigate to the books, take a moment to read
    the descriptions of each navigational section to get a solid understanding
    of why the course is broken up the way it is.</p>

    <h2 class="center">
      Segments of <%= @course.title %>
    </h2>

    <p class="center">A Segment is a focused area of growth within the course. Segments
    are designed to help you work your way towards mastery in a key part of
    physical health, one at a time. Instead of being overwhelmed with everything
    at once, Segments let you dive deep into specific themes.</p>

    <p class="center">Every Segment builds real, lasting change by combining knowledge, practice,
